4 HR____ HONORING MRS. CLYDE LEE ON THE OCCASION OF HER 90TH
5 BIRTHDAY.
6
7 WHEREAS, highest commendations and congratulations
8 are proudly presented to Mrs. Clyde Lee on the occasion of
9 her 90th Birthday; and
10 WHEREAS, Clyde Lee, a cherished family member,
11 friend, and community pillar, has reached the remarkable
12 milestone of 90 years; this milestone occasion is a
13 testament to a life rich in experience, wisdom, and love;
14 and
15 WHEREAS, she has exemplified dedication, grace, and
16 resilience, leaving an indelible mark on all who have had
17 the privilege of knowing her; and
18 WHEREAS, Mrs. Clyde Lee's journey has been filled
19 with family and love; she has shared her life with her
20 cherished husband, Max, and she enjoys spending time with
21 her 10 grandchildren and 16 great-grandchildren; and
22 WHEREAS, she relishes in making beautiful music with
23 her husband; she shows her care for others by tirelessly
24 cooking for those she loves; as a believer in the Lord, she
25 leads a Christian life; and
26 WHEREAS, the milestone of the 90th Birthday is a
27 cause for great rejoicing; it is a tremendous privilege to
28 recognize Mrs. Lee and uplift such a remarkable woman on the
